<p><strong>Skills</strong> Perception +3</p>

<p><strong>Challenge</strong> 1 (200 XP)</p>

<p><strong><em>Keen Smell.</em></strong> The bear has advantage on Wisdom (Perception) checks that rely on smell.</p>

<p><strong>Actions</strong></p>

<p><strong><em>Multiattack.</em></strong> The bear makes two attacks: one with its bite and one with its claws.</p>

<p><strong><em>Bite.</em></strong> Weapon Attack: +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 8 (1d8 + 4) piercing damage.</p>

<p><strong><em>Claws.</em></strong> Melee Weapon Attack: +5 to hit, reach 5 ft., one target. Hit: 11 (2d6 + 4) slashing damage.</p>

